headline.print_headline: Rosberg Leads Hamilton in Opening Practice for Japanese GP
headline.main: Rosberg Leads Hamilton in Opening Practice for Japanese GP

lead_paragraph: Nico Rosberg bounced back from his Singapore disappointment by setting the fastest time in opening practice for Sunday's Japanese Grand Prix.
